OL,3,CAndy Burnham's By-election and mayoral
OL,4,Crace could cost taxpayers #5m
OL,6,FThe combined costs of running a
OL,7,Fmayoral election in Greater Manchester
OL,8,Fand the by-election which could allow
OL,9,FAndy Burnham a return to Westminster
OL,10,Fmay reach #5 million.
OL,12,FThe Mayor of Greater Manchester
OL,13,Fannounced on Thursday evening his
OL,14,Fintention to stand in the Makerfield
OL,15,Fby-election.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
