OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1779030723
OL,3,CAndy Burnham's By-election and mayoral
OL,4,Crace could cost taxpayers #5m
OL,6,FJosh Simons, Labour MP for the seat,
OL,7,Fannounced his resignation earlier the
OL,8,Fsame day to give Mr Burnham a chance
OL,9,Fat a Westminster return, where he
OL,10,Fcould challenge Sir Keir Starmer in a
OL,11,Fbid to become Labour leader and Prime
OL,12,FMinister.
OL,14,FMr Burnham needs to go through an
OL,15,Finternal Labour process to seek
OL,16,Fselection as the party's candidate for
OL,17,FMakerfield.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
