PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1779030723
OL,3,CAndy Burnham's By-election and mayoral
OL,4,Crace could cost taxpayers #5m
OL,6,FWere he to win the by-election, it
OL,7,Fwould trigger the prospect of a poll
OL,8,Fin Greater Manchester to decide who
OL,9,Fwould replace him as the region's
OL,10,Fmayor.
OL,12,FThe Greater Manchester Combined
OL,13,FAuthority said that the cost of the
OL,14,Fprevious mayoral election in 2024 was
OL,15,F#4,719,754.
OL,17,FIn the Makerfield ballot, the official
OL,18,Fresponsible for overseeing the
OL,19,Felection has a budget of #226,208 to
OL,20,Fadministrate it.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1779030723
OL,3,CAndy Burnham's By-election and mayoral
OL,4,Crace could cost taxpayers #5m
OL,6,FSome #3,738 of this will be available
OL,7,Fto pay the lead official, the
OL,8,Freturning officer, for their time.
OL,10,FThe remaining #222,470 is available to
OL,11,Fpay for ballot papers, IT, staffing
OL,12,Fand other support to carry out the
OL,13,Fpoll.
OL,15,FFurther costs to the public purse
OL,16,Fwould be incurred via the postage
OL,17,Fcosts each candidate is entitled to,
OL,18,Fwhich allows them to write to all
OL,19,Fvoting households.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
