PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1779030723
OL,3,CAndy Burnham's By-election and mayoral
OL,4,Crace could cost taxpayers #5m
OL,6,FMinisters revealed in 2016 that the
OL,7,Faverage cost of running a by-election
OL,8,Fsince 2010 was #228,964.This is likely
OL,9,Fto have risen in the intervening
OL,10,Fperiod with inflation.
OL,12,FCommunities Secretary Steve Reed was
OL,13,Fasked by Times Radio on Friday whether
OL,14,Fthe costs of running the by-election
OL,15,Fand a mayoral poll represented good
OL,16,Fvalue for money.
OL,18,FHe told the broadcaster it was "for
OL,19,Fthe people" to judge, adding: "We have
OL,20,Fdemocracy, and democracy does cost
OL,21,Fsome money."
OL,26,@zD@`OU{D@KO]{D@_OU}D@LO]
